[32m│[0m ## Summary                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I've encountered a persistent issue with the `pw_send_payload` tool when     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m trying to send form-encoded POST data to the `/token` endpoint. Despite      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m multiple attempts with various formatting approaches:                        [32m│[0m
