[32m│[0m 1. **Different Content-Type headers** - application/x-www-form-urlencoded,   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m application/json                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **Various header combinations** - with and without Origin, Referer,       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Accept headers                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Different body formats** - with/without grant_type, with/without        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Content-Length                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. **Multiple encoding approaches** - plain form data, URL-encoded values    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m All attempts resulted in the same error:                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```json                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m {"detail":[                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   {"type":"missing","loc":["body","username"],"msg":"Field                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m required","input":null},                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   {"type":"missing","loc":["body","password"],"msg":"Field                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m required","input":null}                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ]}                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The `"input":null` indicates the server is not receiving any POST body at    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m all, suggesting an issue with how Playwright processes and forwards          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m form-encoded POST bodies to FastAPI's OAuth2PasswordRequestForm.             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **What I discovered:**                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ The `/` endpoint returns a login form pointing to POST `/token`         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ The OpenAPI schema confirms `/token` expects                            [32m│[0m
