[32m│[0m - ✅ Other endpoints like `/ping` work correctly                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ✅ GET requests work fine                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ❌ POST requests with form-encoded bodies are not being parsed correctly   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m by the server                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
